Thorley Walters https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thorley_Walters 0 Thorley Swinstead Walters (12 May 1913 – 6 July 1991) was an English character actor. He is probably best remembered for his comedy film roles such as in Two-Way Stretch and Carlton-Browne of the FO.
